        <h1 id="h1-waitlist" style="margin-top:40px;">Sugarbowl Waitlist</h1>
        <br>
        <p class="lead"><b>Welcome to our Waitlist App!</b></p>
        <p><b>For the FAQ, please pay attention to statements in 'bold' font.</b></p>
        <br>
        <h2>FAQ</h2>
        <ol>
            <li><a href="#view_the_waitlist" style="color:#0094FF;">View the Waitlist</a></li>
