        <h3>The Guest's Waitlist Experience</h3>
        <br>
        <div style="text-align:left;">
        <p>To join the Waitlist, the Guest:</p>
        <ol>
            <li>Connects to Wi-Fi or uses cell phone data.</li>
            <li>Scans the <b>QR Code</b> or enters the <b>URL</b> <a href='http://bit.ly/sugarwait' target='_blank' style="color:#0094FF;">bit.ly/sugarwait</a> for the Waitlist into their browser. <b><em>(If the app hasn't been used in 30 min, it goes to sleep and takes a longer time to load back up. The same is true for the app's interface for Sugarbowl staff.)</em></b></li>
            <li>Submits the Guest version of the 'Create New' form.</li>
                <ul>
                    <li>The form directs them to their Wait Session Details (the Guest version). <b>The page displays their Position on the waitlist</b> (e.g. 2 of 5), contact info, etc. <b>They are asked to bookmark this page to track their progress</b> in the waitlist (Figure 1).</li>
                </ul>
            <br>

